    {
        "content": "<p><span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"275920\">John Baez</span> <a href=\"#narrow/stream/229136-theory.3A-category-theory/topic/Question.20about.20a.20subcategory.20of.20comma.20categories/near/326967447\">said</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Is this the pullback in the category Cat of </p>\n<p>$C \\stackrel{S}{\\longrightarrow} D \\stackrel{T}{\\longleftarrow} E $</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Yes.</p>\n<p>Strict 2-pullbacks in the 2-category of categories coincide with ordinary pullbacks in the 1-category of categories.</p>",
